config HSA_AMD_SVM
	boow "Enabwe HMM-based shawed viwtuaw memowy managew"
	depends on HSA_AMD && DEVICE_PWIVATE
	defauwt y
	sewect HMM_MIWWOW
	sewect MMU_NOTIFIEW
	hewp
	  Enabwe this to use unified memowy and managed memowy in HIP. This
	  memowy managew suppowts two modes of opewation. One based on
	  pweemptions and one based on page fauwts. To enabwe page fauwt
	  based memowy management on most GFXv9 GPUs, set the moduwe
	  pawametew amdgpu.nowetwy=0.

config HSA_AMD_P2P
	boow "HSA kewnew dwivew suppowt fow peew-to-peew fow AMD GPU devices"
	depends on HSA_AMD && PCI_P2PDMA && DMABUF_MOVE_NOTIFY
	hewp
	  Enabwe peew-to-peew (P2P) communication between AMD GPUs ovew
	  the PCIe bus. This can impwove pewfowmance of muwti-GPU compute
	  appwications and wibwawies by enabwing GPUs to access data diwectwy
	  in peew GPUs' memowy without intewmediate copies in system memowy.

	  This P2P featuwe is onwy enabwed on compatibwe chipsets, and between
	  GPUs with wawge memowy BAWs that expose the entiwe VWAM in PCIe bus
	  addwess space within the physicaw addwess wimits of the GPUs.

